ru.sportbetsbattle.games

Class Games

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.sportbetsbattle.core.BaseEntity
      • ru.sportbetsbattle.games.Games

  • @Entity
public class Games
extends BaseEntity
    Class which describes each sport event, no matter what kind of sport. Each field is field in data base
    Since:
    1.1
    Version:
    1.1 nameOfTheGame - String: Not null; For example Football, Hockey, Tennis league - String: Not null; FIFA, Wimbledon teamFirst - String: Not null; First team of this game teamSecond - String: Not null; Second team of this game scoreTeamFirst - String: Score of the first team scoreTeamSecond - String: Score of the second team List values - List of scores of THIS game; Each 10 second will update CreatedAt - Date - When the match started; LastUpdated - Date - Last update of the game;
